 failed | not_run\",\n  \"remaining_risks\": [],\n  \"ready_for_evaluation\": true\n}\n```\n\n## Stop Conditions\n\nStop when validation passes, validation fails outside scope, a blocker exists, or evaluator review is needed.\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
